- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning techniques for natural language processing tasks. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely as the paper does not deal with cryptography or security. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also less likely as the paper does not deal with computer vision tasks.
